        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "I have a form with 2 optional ('required' => false) elements.\nWhen I call $myForm->isValid(), I received an Zend_File_Transfer_Exception (\"my_element\" not found by file transfer adapter).\nWhen I traced the exception, Zend_Fom::isValid call Zend_Form_Element_File::isValid which call Zend_Form_Element_File::_getFiles to begin without parameter $noexception even if option 'ignoreNoFile' is set to true.\n\nTested with trunk SVN 13803"
        },
